spanGrp.span: ‘The road to Buenos Aires, Ujarraz-Buenos Aires.
Ñala se dö-glö-mĩũ Buenos Aires Ujarras-Buenos Aires
and come to the bridge uh…
Y se mãu dö-mĩ puente mel ss…
the bridge on the Ceibo River.
We go by; we go by and on.
We take the road and go by; we get to a place called Soköbata;
(_) se të í guge-ra damãu-mĩ damãu-mĩ dö-ka-nẽ pe të kã' du-lë-ka kie Soköbata
it goes till the pinapple plantation.
mãu-mĩ dagaũ eee… pe *të [wã] piña ke-lë
The road gets to Salitre Road;
jera se të guge jula… jula shulë wa
It takes you to Buenos Aires.’
